lodepng
------------------------------------------
PNG image decoder and encoder

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.1-1
  libgcc1-12.4.0-3
  liblodepng-devel-0+git20250402-1bl1
  liblodepng0-0+git20250402-1bl1
  libstdc++6-12.4.0-3
  pkg-config-2.4.3-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.44-1
  cmake-3.28.3-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  gcc-core-12.4.0-3
  gcc-g++-12.4.0-3
  ninja-1.12.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/lvandeve/lodepng

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/lvandeve/lodepng.git

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack lodepng-0+git20250402-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./lodepng-0+git20250402-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/lodepng-0+git20250402-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/lodepng-0+git20250402-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liblodepng0-0+git20250402-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liblodepng-devel-0+git20250402-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(lodepng)
  /usr/bin/pngdetail.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/lodepng.README
  /usr/share/doc/lodepng/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/lodepng/README.md

(liblodepng0)
  /usr/bin/cyglodepng-0.dll

(liblodepng-devel)
  /usr/include/lodepng.h
  /usr/lib/liblodepng.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/lodepng.pc

------------------

